"{\"uid\": \"chroniclelive.co.uk-news-north-east-news-wallsend-wieghtliting-olympic-academy-council-29818742\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Plans have been submitted to convert an empty Wallsend industrial unit into an \\\"Olympic weightlifting academy\\\".\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 111, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"North TynesideCouncil has received an application to convert Unit 18 in the Maurice Road Industrial estate into a weightlifting space.\", \"from\": 113, \"to\": 247, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The firm behind the application, Cube Weightlifting Academy, has stated they now need a permanent hub, having previously traded in shared gym spaces, due to high demand.\", \"from\": 248, \"to\": 417, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 286, \"end\": 299, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Powerlifting\", \"score\": 0.9947114309497449, \"rank\": 0.005316686711069827, \"text\": \"Weightlifting\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Powerlifting\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Powerlifting\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to the application, the weightlifting academy has been trading from shared gym spaces but are finding a \\\"high demand\\\" for its services and are in need of its own property to serve the community.\", \"from\": 419, \"to\": 623, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The academy is affiliated to British Weightlifting and received funding for its youth weightlifting club which targets youth from deprived areas so the academy can offer sessions and equipment at less cost.\", \"from\": 624, \"to\": 830, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 653, \"end\": 660, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999856054925308, \"rank\": 1.3094532273260834e-05, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 661, \"end\": 674, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Powerlifting\", \"score\": 0.9947114309497449, \"rank\": 0.005316686711069827, \"text\": \"Weightlifting\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Powerlifting\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Powerlifting\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The application went on: \\\"We are developing the sport for the local area and are in the top five clubs for youth lifters.\", \"from\": 832, \"to\": 953, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We have athletes in the national GB team and many on the British Weightlifting talent pathway to be in these groups.\\\"\", \"from\": 954, \"to\": 1071, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1011, \"end\": 1018, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999856054925308, \"rank\": 1.3094532273260834e-05, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The application continued: \\\"Our proposal will benefit the local area which many of our members are already from by being able to offer our own safe space and to offer our services more widely to the community.\\\"\", \"from\": 1073, \"to\": 1283, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Cube Weightlifting also state that three other sites, two inWallsendand one inWhitley Bay, had also been considered but were ruled out over rent prices, disabled access, or conflicts of interest.\", \"from\": 1285, \"to\": 1480, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1290, \"end\": 1303, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Powerlifting\", \"score\": 0.9947114309497449, \"rank\": 0.005316686711069827, \"text\": \"Weightlifting\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Powerlifting\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Powerlifting\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"75 Park View, Whitley Bay, had previously hosted Taekwondo and martial arts classes.\", \"from\": 1481, \"to\": 1565, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1495, \"end\": 1506, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Whitley_Bay\", \"score\": 0.9999999321028122, \"rank\": 6.789657429041264e-08, \"text\": \"Whitley Bay\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Whitley_Bay\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Whitley_Bay\"}, {\"begin\": 1530, \"end\": 1539, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taekwondo\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 1.0747262819924019e-13, \"text\": \"Taekwondo\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taekwondo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taekwondo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the time of writing, the application had not been decided on, however, the local authority's highways department has recommended the project go ahead.\", \"from\": 1567, \"to\": 1720, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Join our Breaking News and Top Stories WhatsApp communityfor all the latest news direct to your phone.\", \"from\": 1722, \"to\": 1824, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1731, \"end\": 1744, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Breaking_news\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.034605147685258e-17, \"text\": \"Breaking News\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Breaking_news\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Breaking_news\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To join you need to have WhatsApp on your device.\", \"from\": 1826, \"to\": 1875, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1851, \"end\": 1859, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"score\": 0.974981386291744, \"rank\": 0.025660606510158637, \"text\": \"WhatsApp\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All you need to do is choose which community you want to join, click on the link and press 'join community'.\", \"from\": 1876, \"to\": 1984, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \